  "title": "English Relief Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />We are looking for an English Relief Teacher to conduct Secondary School English lessons on an ad-hoc basis. The role involves stepping in when required to ensure lesson continuity and effective classroom management.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliver Secondary School English lessons based on provided materials</p></li><li><p>Manage classroom and engage students effectively</p></li><li><p>Support lesson continuity in the absence of the regular teacher</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in English, Education, or related field</p></li><li><p>Experience teaching Secondary School English preferred</p></li><li><p>Responsible, adaptable, and professional</p></li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ad-hoc assignments based on scheduling needs</p></li><li><p>Teaching materials will be provided</p></li></ul>",
