    "description": "<p>HANBRIDGE INSTITUTE PTE LTD</p><p>Since its establishment in 2003, Hanbridge Institute has grown from a one-classroom entity to an Institution of excellence, proving courses from English tuition to government preparatory courses at primary and secondary levels.</p><p>Adhering to the stated core values of excellence, harmony, care and concern, and innovation, Hanbridge Institute has delivered on the stated mission of helping hundreds of youths realize their potential and achieve their dreams in life.</p><p>Situated at Fragrance Empire Building, we offer a conducive learning environment for all our students. In addition, we are also a stone’s throw away from the Labrador Park MRT station, popular shopping centre Vivocity and the vibrant art district of Gillman Barracks.</p><p>At Hanbridge, we understand that hardware is only one part of students’ learning experience. Being able to provide them with care, support, and hands-on guidance is critical in optimizing their educational journey with us.</p><p>As such, we are stringent in the selection of our teachers, who are all equipped with the relevant professional and educational qualifications, and registered with SkillsFuture Singapore (SSG). Together with our dedicated support staff, we aim to provide a complete and unforgettable learning experience with Hanbridge.</p>",
